rgin:0pt 0pt 9.8pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">In general terms, our points of contact with the GMC have been positive.  Our interaction with the GMC as regards revalidation has been good and the process appears to be running smoothly.  In addition, communications with the GMC as regards fitness to practise and other sanctions have been very helpful.</span></li><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 9.8pt 32pt; padding-left:4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">We have experienced a more negative interaction with the GMC in the area of curricula with delays in feedback/approval of curriculum changes.  However, contact as regards training and quality assurance has been satisfactory.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">November 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:right"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">1</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>